{"tid":1954825,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【天文】你生日那天的宇宙","createTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T07:28:36.000Z","uid":72909,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"848803734c20ae8f04720eecb255974f18eb267d","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">各位巴絲，可以關注返呢個文藝專頁，好多好野睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%80%9D%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%258C%2596&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUiQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=f9e99b52\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%80%9D%E5%8C%96</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@night_wing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40night_wing&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUiQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=c51625bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@night_wing</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有錯麻煩大家幫我補充，同埋希望大家Quote文唔好Quote全篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n----------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jbt8k4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbt8k4z.jpg&h=7a300574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家未必認識哈勃，但你一定聽過以佢命名嘅望遠鏡：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>哈勃太空望遠鏡 Hubble Space Telescope</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mXQzpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mXQzpz.jpg&h=18a83f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢支喺1990年4月24日，由美國太空總署 <span style=\"color: gold;\">N</span>ational <span style=\"color: gold;\">A</span>eronautics and <span style=\"color: gold;\">S</span>pace <span style=\"color: gold;\">A</span>dministration (NASA) 同歐洲太空總署 <span style=\"color: orange;\">E</span>uropean <span style=\"color: orange;\">S</span>pace <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>gency (ESA) 合作發射嘅望遠鏡，屈指一算，已經運行咗29年11個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/im1RiRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fim1RiRe.png&h=05748094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n適逢30週年，NASA就係網站開咗左個叫「Your Birthday Image」嘅分頁。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/what-did-hubble-see-on-your-birthday\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fcontent%2Fgoddard%2Fwhat-did-hubble-see-on-your-birthday&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUiQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=3ff10b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/what-did-hubble-see-on-your-birthday</a><br />\n大家只要簡返自己嘅生日日期(係冇年份簡嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，就可以睇到個日由哈勃影低嘅相片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但由於網站讀取速度實在太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以我會同大家整合，再順便介紹。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------------------</span>"},{"pid":"c8052e2420dfba7cbcbab53a2ab66f6acf1c01cf","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">連登又食咗我兩篇草稿，而家重新打過...</span>"},{"pid":"9b9a7905b3c1b17d318be39d7f79c11e5f1eb574","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">正式開始，會順序咁介紹落去。<br />\np.s. 整理時發現365張相入面有唔小都係重覆，有小小可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------------------<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">1月1日</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsKrTAp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsKrTAp.png&h=ee27c8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拍攝於2012，位於銀河系獅子座方向，距離地球500,000光年嘅 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>獅子座IV Galaxy Leo IV</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"604febecc04f152d794b07cac11283b0b12f94a8","tid":1954825,"uid":137871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"終於出新po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e4773d8afe50768dcd40af928c356e472283ce","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:08:31.000Z","msg":"開柒咗，晏Ｄ再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba738e6fbdbe481185bb8dff48122b07657f5374","tid":1954825,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e4773d8afe50768dcd40af928c356e472283ce","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:08:31.000Z","msg":"開柒咗，晏Ｄ再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"晏啲再留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f9a979e763b448c7f53e94e1bcecb535596568","tid":1954825,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1954926/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1954926/page/1</a>"}]}